{
  "text": "The classes of all harmonic starlike functions of order \u03b1 and harmonic convex functions of order \u03b1 are denoted by S * H (\u03b1) and K H (\u03b1), respectively. These classes have been extensively studied by Jahangiri [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
